# ============================================================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES
# ============================================================================

# REMINDER: Never commit:
# 1. HubSpot API tokens (HUBSPOT_TOKEN in Config file)
# 2. Spreadsheet IDs (if hardcoded)
# 3. Client-specific data
# 4. Personal access tokens
# 5. OAuth credentials
# 6. Any file containing actual company/customer data

# BEFORE COMMITTING:
# 1. Search for 'pat-na1-' (HubSpot token prefix)
# 2. Search for actual company names
# 3. Search for email addresses
# 4. Search for 'TODO' and 'FIXME' if workflow requires
# 5. Review diff carefully

